'''''Merte''''' was a [[Hurrim]] [[Lambda-class T-4a shuttle/Legends|''Lambda''-class T-4a shuttle]]. It was hijacked by two members of [[Dunari]]'s smuggler coalition. The ''Merte'' fled into a civilian spaceport called [[Camen Spaceport]], where it met up with two [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[RZ-1 A-wing interceptor/Legends|RZ-1 A-wing interceptors]] from the [[Mon Calamari Star Cruiser/Legends|Mon Calamari Star Cruiser]] [[Liberty/Legends|''Liberty'']], one of them being flown by [[Ace Azzameen/Legends|Ace Azzameen]]. The Rebels defended their allies from a Hurrim pursuit team and managed to escort them back to the [[Liberty/Legends|''Liberty'']] after evading several traps.

